loss></mentioned>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">It is related to a group of words (<ref type="xr" target="#entry_qæppæl"/> ‘clothes’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_cūpal"/> ‘bunch’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_gæbaz"/> ‘shred’ etc.), considered under <ref type="xr" target="#entry_tymbyl"/> ‘round’. The original relation to <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/> <w>kambala-</w> <gloss><q>blanket</q></gloss></mentioned> is possible.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>